    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/88e793cdd739b8bd382844daaae64758.poster.avif?t=1767864344\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/88e793cdd739b8bd382844daaae64758.webm?t=1767864344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/88e793cdd739b8bd382844daaae64758.mp4?t=1767864344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to step onto the field with your Toyz?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world filled with small, living, magical creatures, Toyz teams clash in action-packed battles featuring unique abilities and special powers. The goal is simple: combine strategy, flashy combat, and powerful moves to score more goals than your opponents and claim victory in the Toyz tournament!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/b71d52c5eea9d2781dda3b14389a7e42.webp?t=1767864344\" width=620 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/b0b822d74c3d731f7b8f75e0d11eaac1.avif?t=1767864344\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras_big/b0b822d74c3d731f7b8f75e0d11eaac1.avif?t=1767864344 width=800 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are so many Toyz, and each one has unique abilities! Combine their powers to craft winning strategies and defeat the opposing team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/4ba1d10debf22f2c31742cbc7b4e00cb.webp?t=1767864344\" width=616 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/3b1c413df398e1c87eef5cfd89ee917a.poster.avif?t=1767864344\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/3b1c413df398e1c87eef5cfd89ee917a.webm?t=1767864344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/3b1c413df398e1c87eef5cfd89ee917a.mp4?t=1767864344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Once the ultimate is activated, a giant Robot is unleashed and the player can receive assistance, alter the environment, defend a location, receive a boost, and more! The Robots are collectibles that you unlock by completing quests. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/ac7f8d31fdfcf2e6b35c8e9c93d3dd0e.webp?t=1767864344\" width=620 height=25 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/e8e79c819397dcd940d6b8cc33bb2f81.poster.avif?t=1767864344\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/e8e79c819397dcd940d6b8cc33bb2f81.webm?t=1767864344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/e8e79c819397dcd940d6b8cc33bb2f81.mp4?t=1767864344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore the strange world of Earth through the eyes of the stranded aliens. Meet oddball NPCs, take on their challenges, and unlock new characters with unique abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/54d3ab76d8b70e3a8f36d7c9a7c9c188.webp?t=1767864344\" width=620 height=25 /></span>We are a small indie studio located in the south of Switzerland with great ambition and skills. Momento Games specializes in game-as-a-service with the mission of enabling players and content creators to interact like never before through the development of innovative technology. Stuck On Earth is our debut title and a testament to the future we are building. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273530/extras/8055c53c7ebff05616b29bec9dc73858.avif?t=1767864344\" width=620 height=450 /></span></p>",
